Subject: Open Source Martial Arts
Description: There are a great many martial artists here at PenguiCon!  Come on down and work on some problem solving together!  Learn about the similarities and differences between European, Chinese, Japanese, Filipino, Indonesian, Malaysian, and all other martial arts styles!  Traditional, non-traditional, all are welcome here!  Speakers include:Kent Newland - Track: Action Adventure  - Duration: 1 hour and 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
